reviewText: I have two little girls who love Christmas movies and will watch almost anything to do with Christmas. It kept my 4 year olds attention, but not my 2 year old. Quality is pretty poor and I honestly don't remember the storyline. Put it on for the kids when you need to get some stuff done...if it holds their attention.

I purchased this for a toddler, but it is a movie for the whole family, no matter what age.  It even teaches the mice about the First Christmas and the Holy Family.  Make it a part of your holiday collection.
